OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FPatchy rain
OL,6,Fclearing the east this evening then
OL,7,Fdrier for a time. Cloud thickening
OL,8,Fagain overnight with some rain or
OL,9,Fdrizzle returning during the early
OL,10,Fhours.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FCloudy with occasional rain
OL,13,Fin the morning then brightening up
OL,14,Fwith a few showers in the afternoon.
OL,15,FPersistent rain retiring from the west
OL,16,Ffrom late afternoon onwards.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
